they're after us.

22:12.667 --> 22:14.026
No, they're here, too.

22:14.126 --> 22:15.026
I can hear them.

22:15.126 --> 22:17.067
As long as we have the key,

22:17.167 --> 22:18.859
Thistle is safe.

22:18.959 --> 22:21.901
So just, uh, stay there and,

22:22.001 --> 22:23.650
and turn on all the lights

22:23.750 --> 22:25.399
