like a pretty nasty fall.

24:07.376 --> 24:09.026
Yeah, Cole, we're,
we're fine, really.

24:09.126 --> 24:10.775
You two seem different.

24:10.875 --> 24:11.609
Different?

24:11.709 --> 24:12.109
I mean,

24:12.209 --> 24:13.734
I thought maybe you were,
I don't know,

24:13.834 --> 24:16.650
drunk or something before,
but now you seem...

24:16.750 --> 24:17.625
Sober.

24:19.001 --> 24:22.292
Stairs can be... sobering.

24:24.499 --> 24:26.399
Right. Okay, um,

24:26.499 --> 24:27.734
I'm really sorry

24:27.834 --> 24:32.376
