I really am.

24:36.251 --> 24:39.499
No worries. I'll keep trying.

24:42.750 --> 24:44.859
Stairs can be sobering?

24:44.959 --> 24:46.775
Okay, what was I supposed
to say?

24:46.875 --> 24:49.399
That some unknown demon came in
to try and steal our magic book,

24:49.499 --> 24:52.567
and then little trolls came
and pushed us down the stairs?

24:52.667 --> 24:56.234
Right. Okay, but why
are we thinking like grownups

24:56.334 --> 24:56.787
all of a sudden?

24:56.797 --> 25:01.276
I don't know. It must have been
from the trauma of the attack.

25:01.376 --> 25:03.151
Which is probably
a really good thing

25:03.251 --> 25:04.942
because I don't really think
that our inner children

25:05.042 --> 25:06.399
would have a lot of luck
protecting Kate.

25:06.499 --> 25:08.399
And now that the trolls have
the key,

25:08.499 --> 25:10.917
we really need
to go protect Kate.

25:11.875 --> 25:15.499
Uh, hello, Prue?

25:16.376 --> 25:18.901
Okay, I don't
understand why

25:19.001 --> 25:21.318
we just don't get
to Kate.

25:21.418 --> 25:22.525
Well, because with
the dust worn off,

25:22.625 --> 25:23.537
we won't be able
to see the trolls.

25:23.547 --> 25:25.567
Okay, well,
I already looked in
<i>The Book of Shadows</i>

25:25.667 --> 25:27.318
and there's nothing
in there about trolls.

25:27.418 --> 25:29.483
I know.
I'm thinking of piecing together

25:29.583 --> 25:31.399
a makeshift spell like, uh,

25:31.499 --> 25:32.026
here--

25:32.126 --> 25:34.609
um, "To see what
can't be seen."

25:34.709 --> 25:35.942
If we combine that one
with the one

25:36.042 --> 25:38.859
to cultivate innocence
and the power-of-three spell,

25:38.959 --> 25:39.578
it just might work.

25:39.588 --> 25:41.525
That's why
you're the older sister.

25:41.625 --> 25:43.151
You are always thinking.

25:43.251 --> 25:43.662
Thank you.

25:43.672 --> 25:44.609
All right, I'll work
on the spell.

25:44.709 --> 25:46.667
Why don't you go call
Piper, okay?

25:47.625 --> 25:48.984
Um...

25:49.084 --> 25:49.984
what's the point
of that?

25:50.084 --> 25:51.399
Isn't she still
on the picket line?

25:51.499 --> 25:53.692
Yeah, but we can't fight
the trolls without her.

25:53.792 --> 25:55.067
I mean, they're just too fast.

25:55.167 --> 25:56.234
