but now we actually need her.

26:01.499 --> 26:02.399
Okay.

26:02.499 --> 26:03.620
Uh, hey, watch out for doorways
and stuff,

26:03.630 --> 26:05.775
because now that
the trolls know that
we're helping Kate,

26:05.875 --> 26:08.442
they'll do everything they can
to stop all three of us.

26:08.542 --> 26:10.499
Mm-hmm.

