believe in fairies,

26:48.459 --> 26:49.400
and I'm not asking you to.

26:49.500 --> 26:50.609
Then what are you asking?

26:50.709 --> 26:52.318
We were trying
to distract you before.

26:52.418 --> 26:54.859
We were trying to take your mind
off of Leo, okay?

26:54.959 --> 26:55.775
And it was wrong,

26:55.875 --> 26:56.775
and I'm sorry for that.

26:56.875 --> 26:58.525
But it's not about that
anymore, Piper.

26:58.625 --> 27:02.901
