we cannot fight without you.

27:03.001 --> 27:04.318
Trolls?

27:04.418 --> 27:05.399
Believe it or don't,

27:05.499 --> 27:06.525
but they are sneaky and mean

27:06.625 --> 27:11.042
and they're trying to hurt
a seven-year-old girl.

27:12.542 --> 27:13.692
Hello?

27:13.792 --> 27:15.525
Any chance
they may have been here?

27:15.625 --> 27:19.192
Yeah, one attacked me
there earlier, why?

27:19.292 --> 27:20.483
Nothing.

27:20.583 --> 27:22.609
All right, look,
they know that we're witches,

27:22.709 --> 27:25.399
and they will do anything
to stop us from helping Kate.

27:25.499 --> 27:27.234
All right, all right.
I'm on my way.

27:27.334 --> 27:29.151
Okay, well,
don't forget to stay

27:29.251 --> 27:29.942
out of the...

27:30.042 --> 27:32.192
(<i>click, dial tone</i>)

27:32.292 --> 27:35.334
...tween places.

27:39.709 --> 27:42.442
Abbey, have you seen my keys?

27:42.542 --> 27:43.318
Aren't they on the hook?

27:43.418 --> 27:46.359
No, if they were on the hook,
I wouldn't be asking.

27:46.459 --> 27:48.609
(<i>troll growling</i>)

27:48.709 --> 27:50.399
Oh, I got it, I got it!

27:50.499 --> 27:52.459
Oh, damn it!

27:53.750 --> 27:57.650
Spare key, spare key.

27:57.750 --> 27:58.483
Register.

27:58.583 --> 28:00.399
(<i>troll growls</i>)

28:00.499 --> 28:00.901
Ow!

28:01.001 --> 28:01.942
(<i>gasps</i>)

28:02.042 --> 28:03.399
Son of a...!

28:03.499 --> 28:04.399
Oh, are you okay?

28:04.499 --> 28:09.901
Uh, would you just do me a favor
and close up for me?

28:10.001 --> 28:11.775
Oh, yeah, sure.

28:11.875 --> 28:13.792
Thank you.

28:24.917 --> 28:27.334
(<i>troll growling</i>)

28:33.667 --> 28:34.483
(<i>shrieks</i>)

28:34.583 --> 28:36.399
(<i>troll laughing</i>)

28:36.499 --> 28:37.483
Oh!

28:37.583 --> 28:44.418
You better run while you can,
you little rodents.

28:45.499 --> 28:50.026
I bet you guys think
this is real funny, don't you?

28:50.126 --> 28:51.151
Haven't you taken enough
from me?

28:51.251 --> 28:56.109
